Notice No. CMS-19

March 4, 2002


NOTICE OF INTENTION TO SWITCH QUALIFYING CLEARING MEMBER


        Please be advised that effective immediately Man International, Inc.

will no longer guarantee the following Member(s):


Christopher Puglisi (PUGS-3197)

Richard Morelli (RPM-4301)

William LoRusso (WLO-3552)


However, the above mentioned will remain a member(s) guaranteed by F.C.

Stone, LLC.


        Members and Member Firms have ten (10) days from the date of this

notice to advise the Membership Department of any claims against the

aforementioned Member(s).  Inquiries regarding this matter should be

directed to the Membership Department at <dlowe@nymex.com>.
